    },
    "body": "`DeserializeHDKeypaths()` was writing into the original `hd_keypaths` map instead of `deserialized_hd_keypaths`. As a result the latter was always empty and the round-trip assertion following was trivially true, so the serialize/deserialize round-trip wasn't actually being exercised.\r\n\r\nThat bug was introduced with the commit introducing the fuzz target (commit f898ef65c947776750e49d050633f830546bbdc6, #18994).",
    "labels": [
