          "sha": "27472a542c605df547b957dd947fa301f6efa63a",
          "html_url": "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/27472a542c605df547b957dd947fa301f6efa63a"
        }
      ],
      "message": "fuzz: fix dead HD keypaths (de)serialization round-trip\n\n`DeserializeHDKeypaths()` was writing into the original `hd_keypaths`\nmap instead of `deserialized_hd_keypaths`. As a result the latter was\nalways empty and the round-trip assertion following was trivially true,\nso the serialize/deserialize round-trip wasn't actually being exercised.\n\nThat bug was introduced with the commit introducing the fuzz target\n(commit f898ef65c947776750e49d050633f830546bbdc6, #18994).",
      "committer": {
        "name": "Sebastian Falbesoner",
        "email": "sebastian.falbesoner@gmail.com",
        "date": "2026-06-07T18:56:03Z"
      },
      "author": {
